Package org.jvoicexml.implementation.jsapi10

This package contains basic classes to support JSAPI 1.0 implementations for UserInput and SystemOutput.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
SSMLSpeakStrategy Strategy to play back a node of a SSML document via JSAPI.
 

Class Summary
AudioInput Audio input that uses the JSAPI 1.0 to address the recognition engine.
AudioOutput Audio output that uses the JSAPI 1.0 to address the TTS engine.
Jsapi10RecognitionResult JSAPI 10 implementation of the result of the recognition process.
JVoiceXMLRecognitionListener Thread that waits for input from the recognizer.
RuleGrammarImplementation Implementation of a JSGF grammar.
 

Package org.jvoicexml.implementation.jsapi10 Description

This package contains basic classes to support JSAPI 1.0 implementations for UserInput and SystemOutput.
